programme.title: Lag Ja Gale S1 Ep32
programme.desc: Drama ini mengisahkan perjalanan dua individu yang berbeza latar belakang, Shiv Dhooper, seorang usahawan muda Punjabi yang berjaya, dan Ishani Kulkarni, seorang wanita dari Maharashtra yang bekerja keras untuk menyara keluarganya. Mereka dipertemukan melalui perkahwinan yang diatur untuk membantu adik-beradik mereka, walaupun mereka mempunyai pandangan hidup yang berbeza. Dalam perjalanan mereka, mereka turut menghadapi pelbagai cabaran dan konflik keluarga. Akhirnya, kisah berakhir dengan mereka membina kehidupan bersama, menandakan permulaan kisah cinta mereka yang sebenar.

programme.title: Saatchi S1 Ep4
programme.desc: Kavya, seorang gadis autistik dengan daya ingatan visual yang luar biasa, menjadi saksi kepada pembunuhan Datin Radha dari tingkap biliknya. Walaupun tidak mampu berkomunikasi secara tradisional, Kavya menggunakan lukisannya untuk mendedahkan apa yang berlaku pada malam kejadian. Dengan bantuan Karthik, seorang peguam muda yang bersikap empati tetapi bergelut dengan masalah keluarganya, Kavya berusaha membongkar misteri di sebalik pembunuhan itu.

programme.title: Once Upon A Time In Cyprus S1 Ep8
programme.desc: Mengisahkan tentang seorang lelaki bernama Yusuf, yang terperangkap dalam konflik yang semakin memuncak antara masyarakat Turki dan Yunani di Cyprus. Ketika ketegangan politik semakin meruncing, Yusuf bersama sahabat-sahabatnya harus membuat pilihan yang sukar antara mempertahankan bangsa dan mencari jalan damai. "Once Upon A Time In Cyprus" bukan hanya menceritakan tentang konflik, tetapi juga tentang kekuatan hubungan manusia, cinta dan pengorbanan dalam menghadapi cabaran yang tidak terduga.

programme.desc: Udan, seorang mahasiswa seni idealis yang terlalu obses dengan muzik, jatuh cinta kepada Mendung, mahasiswi farmasi yang bercita-cita tinggi sebagai wanita karier tanpa bergantung pada siapapun. Walaupun cinta mereka kuat, perbezaan impian menyebabkan konflik baharu. Udan mahu mengejar dunia muziknya, manakala Mendung fokus mengejar kerjaya profesional. Kehidupan mereka bertembung dengan sosok Will, seorang lelaki berstatus dan matang yang cuba memikat Mendung.

programme.title: Jendela Hati S1 Ep1
programme.desc: Meskipun Farah sedang menunggu saat diijabkabulkan, namun dia masih dalam dilema untuk menjadi isteri Lukman. Dia masih keliru dengan keputusannya, antara amanah arwah Sarah dengan keikhlasannya menerima abang iparnya sebagai suami. Baik Lukman mahupun Farah, kedua-duanya terpaksa maniskan wajah di majlis pernikahan mereka demi menjaga hati Zahin dan kedua-dua orang tua. Di sebalik kegembiraan, ada hati yang tercarik luka dengan pernikahan mereka. Lantaran terlalu kecewa, Myra sanggup bertindak di luar kawalan hingga menyebabkannya kemalangan dan koma. Joshua muncul untuk membantu Myra lalu membawanya ke hospital. Lukman pula resah kerana tidak dapat menjejak Myra setelah Myra hilang begitu sahaja ketika majlis pernikahannya berlangsung. Farah kecewa apabila Lukman berterus terang yang dia takkan menyentuh Farah kerana dia hanya setia dan cintakan arwah isterinya, Sarah.

programme.title: War Path
programme.desc: Seorang pembunuh kontrak menerima pekerjaan berbahaya yang tidak betul, meletakkan nyawa isterinya dalam bahaya.

programme.title: Black S1 EP4 S1 Ep4
programme.desc: Sebagai tukaran dengan fail ayahnya, Lokman memujuk Sofia untuk bekerja dengannya dan menggunakan kuasa Sofia untuk memberitahunya mana-mana kliennya yang akan menemui ajal. Semasa menjalankan tugas, Sofia bertemu Black yang menyedari kuasa Sofia mungkin kunci untuk membantunya memburu 419. Namun, caranya yang kasar menjengkelkan Sofia dan dia mendapati dirinya tidak diendahkan. Demi memenangi semula hati Sofia, Black menyiasat kes tembakan yang melibatkan Malik untuk meyakinkan Sofia yang dia bukan punca Malik ditembak. Pendirian Sofia berubah menjadi agak lembut dan seterusnya bersetuju untuk membantu Black mendapatkan ingatannya semula. Namun keadaan menjadi rumit apabila Black mengungkai lebih banyak petunjuk tentang kematian Malik dan menyedari nyawanya dalam bahaya.

programme.title: XXX
programme.desc: Kerajaan AS merekrut atlet sukan ekstrem Xander Cage untuk menyusup masuk ke dalam sindiket jenayah Rusia, yang merancang kemusnahan dunia.

programme.title: Obsesi Dia EP1 S1 Ep1
programme.desc: Aafiyah dan Rizq anak kepada pasangan Adelia dan Rafeeq. Aafiyah dimasukkan ke hospital, semasa abangnya menzirahi Aafiyah doktor mengesahkan gadis tersebut mengalami trauma dan lupa ingatan. Sebulan sebelum kejadian, Aafiyah menyambut harijadinya di sebuah hotel tempat ibunya bekerja. Disebabkan kesibukan bekerja, kedua-duanya meninggalkan Aafiyah keseorangan. Aafiyah ternampak seorang bertopeng membunuh seorang wanita, dia yang ketakutan cuba melarikan diri tetapi berjaya ditangkap oleh pembunuh tersebut. Aafiyah berjanji tidak akan membuka rahsia tersebut kepada sesiapa. Aafiyah bersama ibunya berjaya menyelamatkan berkereta keluar dari hotel. Namun pembunuh tersebut berjaya menahan mereka dan membunuh ibunya

programme.title: Kanang Anak Langkau
programme.desc: Sebuah filem berdasarkan kisah benar Sarjan Kanang Anak Langkau, seorang pahlawan iban dan pahlawan perang yang paling terkenal di negara ini, yang berjuang dengan berani semasa pemberontakan komunis.

programme.title: Arjuna S1 Ep6
programme.desc: Amurta yang dalam keadaan nazak diselamatkan oleh Arjuna menggunakan kuasa sakti dan Amutra sembuh tanpa meninggalkan sedikit kesan pun pada badannya. Orang Kaya Sadhya muncul bersama Jagat, dengan beberapa orang untuk menangkap Arjuna tetapi dihalang oleh Amutra yang memberitahu kisah yang sebenar tetapi Orang Kaya Sadhya tidak peduli dan membawa pulang Amurta.

programme.title: Obsesi Dia EP2 S1 Ep2
programme.desc: Mengisahkan Aafiyah kecewa apabila abangnya tidak melayan panggilannya, tambahan pula dia ketakutan dan dalam keadaan trauma. Aafiyah mengalami trauma, dia terpaksa melarikan diri apabila dikejar lelaki misteri dan cuba membunuhnya. Nasib baik Abang Zack muncul dan menyelamatkannya. Aafiyah balik ke rumah setelah sihat. Aafiyah sukakan Zack tetapi bukan sebagi kekasih. Aafiyah sekali lagi menjadi trauma apabila kucing kesayangannya di bunuh. Ini semua angkara Zacky yang menggunakan Rafeeq bagi memuaskan hatinya.

programme.title: Arjuna S1 Ep6
programme.desc: Amurta yang dalam keadaan nazak diselamatkan oleh Arjuna menggunakan kuasa sakti dan Amutra sembuh tanpa meninggalkan sedikit kesan pun pada badannya. Orang Kaya Sadhya muncul bersama Jagat, dengan beberapa orang untuk menangkap Arjuna tetapi dihalang oleh Amutra yang memberitahu kisah yang sebenar tetapi Orang Kaya Sadhya tidak peduli dan membawa pulang Amurta.

programme.title: District 13
programme.desc: Terletak di ghetto Paris pada tahun 2010, seorang polis yang menyamar dan bekas samseng cuba menyusup masuk ke dalam kumpulan untuk meredakan bom neutron.

programme.title: Petaka
programme.desc: Mengisahkan kemiskinan hidup keluarga Sham selepas kematian ayahnya. Ibunya menderita sakit kaki, manakala adiknya, Syikin tidak mampu ke sekolah kerana kekangan kewangan. Kedaifan keluarganya berubah secara drastik apabila Sham menerima tawaran bekerja sebagai pemandu lori barang di kedai perabot Haziq. Tugasnya hanya mengambil dan menghantar barangan perabot dari sempadan Thailand ke kedai Haziq di Alor Setar. Haziq bekerja di bawah Datuk Jamil.

programme.title: Tujuh
programme.desc: Sekumpulan tujuh sahabat yang pernah terlibat dalam satu kejadian tragis bertahun lalu kembali dihantui apabila seorang demi seorang mula mati secara misteri. Dalam usaha mencari kebenaran, mereka mula menyedari bahawa dosa silam mereka tidak akan terampun dan pembalasan sedang menanti.

programme.title: Charismata
programme.desc: Seram psikologi tentang seorang detektif polis yang kewarasannya mula teruji semasa dia menyiasat siri pembunuhan ritualistik yang kejam.

programme.title: Bohsia 2: Jalan Kembali
programme.desc: Tasha (Nabila Huda) ialah seorang gadis yang membesar tanpa keluarga dan pendidikan, memaksanya mencari perlindungan dalam dunia gelap, di kalangan gengster jalanan. Tidak lama kemudian, dia mula bosan dengan kehidupannya yang tiada makna, namun jalan menuju penebusannya penuh dengan pelbagai rintangan.

programme.title: Tujuh
programme.desc: Sekumpulan tujuh sahabat yang pernah terlibat dalam satu kejadian tragis bertahun lalu kembali dihantui apabila seorang demi seorang mula mati secara misteri. Dalam usaha mencari kebenaran, mereka mula menyedari bahawa dosa silam mereka tidak akan terampun dan pembalasan sedang menanti.

programme.title: Obsesi Dia EP1 S1 Ep1
programme.desc: Aafiyah dan Rizq anak kepada pasangan Adelia dan Rafeeq. Aafiyah dimasukkan ke hospital, semasa abangnya menzirahi Aafiyah doktor mengesahkan gadis tersebut mengalami trauma dan lupa ingatan. Sebulan sebelum kejadian, Aafiyah menyambut harijadinya di sebuah hotel tempat ibunya bekerja. Disebabkan kesibukan bekerja, kedua-duanya meninggalkan Aafiyah keseorangan. Aafiyah ternampak seorang bertopeng membunuh seorang wanita, dia yang ketakutan cuba melarikan diri tetapi berjaya ditangkap oleh pembunuh tersebut. Aafiyah berjanji tidak akan membuka rahsia tersebut kepada sesiapa. Aafiyah bersama ibunya berjaya menyelamatkan berkereta keluar dari hotel. Namun pembunuh tersebut berjaya menahan mereka dan membunuh ibunya

programme.title: Obsesi Dia EP2 S1 Ep2
programme.desc: Mengisahkan Aafiyah kecewa apabila abangnya tidak melayan panggilannya, tambahan pula dia ketakutan dan dalam keadaan trauma. Aafiyah mengalami trauma, dia terpaksa melarikan diri apabila dikejar lelaki misteri dan cuba membunuhnya. Nasib baik Abang Zack muncul dan menyelamatkannya. Aafiyah balik ke rumah setelah sihat. Aafiyah sukakan Zack tetapi bukan sebagi kekasih. Aafiyah sekali lagi menjadi trauma apabila kucing kesayangannya di bunuh. Ini semua angkara Zacky yang menggunakan Rafeeq bagi memuaskan hatinya.

programme.title: Kutuk
programme.desc: Maya, seorang jururawat yang baru berpindah ke sebuah asrama lama di pinggir bandar, mula diganggu oleh kejadian aneh dan menyeramkan. Dia kemudian menyedari bahawa asrama itu menyimpan rahsia gelap tentang sumpahan yang menghantui setiap penghuni yang tinggal di situ. Untuk menyelamatkan diri, Maya perlu membongkar misteri di sebalik kutukan tersebut sebelum terlambat.

programme.title: Sembunyi: Amukan Azazil
programme.desc: Aishah, seorang wanita muda zaman penjajahan Jepun, terbangun di sebuah kampung sunyi yang kelihatan tidak terjejas oleh perang. Dia menemui rahsia gelap kampung itu serta makhluk jahat bernama Azazil yang memburu penduduk.

programme.title: Parole Examiner Lee EP3 S1 Ep3

programme.title: Kanang Anak Langkau
programme.desc: Sebuah filem berdasarkan kisah benar Sarjan Kanang Anak Langkau, seorang pahlawan iban dan pahlawan perang yang paling terkenal di negara ini, yang berjuang dengan berani semasa pemberontakan komunis.

programme.title: Parole Examiner Lee EP4 S1 Ep4
programme.desc: Han-shin menyiasat kes banduan yang dipaksa menjadi pengangkut dadah dari dalam penjara. Pergerakannya mula diperhatikan oleh Ji Myeong-seob, pewaris Ojung Group. Tekanan terhadap Han-shin semakin meningkat.

programme.title: The Invoking 2
programme.desc: Walaupun beratus-ratus peristiwa paranormal yang mengganggu berlaku setiap tahun, kebanyakan pertemuan mengerikan ini tidak dilaporkan - sehingga kini. Bersaksilah ketika mangsa malang mengalami ketakutan yang tidak terkata apabila berhadapan dengan kuasa syaitan, poltergeist pembunuh dan entiti jahat lain yang mati bersedia untuk menuntut jiwa mereka . Turun ke jurang mimpi buruk yang terjaga ketika roh-roh jahat yang dahagakan darah ini berusaha untuk memiliki mangsa mereka dan menyeret mereka-menendang dan menjerit-turun ke neraka.

programme.title: Arjuna EP8 S1 Ep8
programme.desc: Dzulkarnain muncul dalam mimpi Arjuna dan menyerapkan ilmu persilatan batin kepadanya. Arjuna dan para pendekar sakti mendapat misi pertama untuk menyelesaikan masalah lelaki 'amuk' yang membunuh ramai penduduk. Namun begitu, lelaki 'amuk' itu hanyalah perangkap Lang Kajai dan Nading untuk memerangkap para pendekar sakti.

programme.title: Tak Kisahlah Beb
programme.desc: Bob, seorang DJ di sebuah kelab malam terkenal dengan sikapnya yang suka mementikngkan diri sendiri selain perangainya yang nakal. Diperangkapnya Rozi, lalu Bob menodai dan meninggalkannya. Pertengkaran berlaku apabila mereka bertemu kembali atas apa yang Bob telah lakukan kepadanya. Setelah disedarkan rakan-rakannya, Bob menyesali tindakannya dan cuba untuk mencari jalan berbaik semula.

programme.title: Pening-Pening Lalat
programme.desc: Dino berjaya melarikan diri dari sebuah penjara dan sedang berada dalam buruan polis. Berita tentangnya mendapat liputan besar dan ditawarkan wang sebanyak RM10,000 kepada sesiapa yang menangkapnya. Mengetahui tentang itu, Dino mula menyembunyikan diri. Memutuskan untuk bersembunyi di hutan, Dino bertemu Zakaria dan Aliza.

programme.title: Janda Meletup
programme.desc: Rosnah, seorang janda muda cuba dipikat oleh Kamil yang tertarik dengannya namun gagal. Samad yang berasal dari Kuala Lumpur pergi ke kampung untuk mencari pembantu rumah dan bertemu Rosnah yang ingin bekerja dengannya. Kamil yang kecewa pergi ke Kuala Lumpur untuk berjumpa Rosnah selain tekadnya yang ingin bekerja dan mengahwini Rosnah. Suatu insiden terjadi menyebabkan Rosnah dan Kamil berganding bahu untuk menyelamatkan Samad.

programme.title: Anaknya Sazali
programme.desc: Sazali tidak mahu anaknya mengamalkan pergaulan bebas sebagaimana yang pernah dilaluinya dahulu. Dia bertindak dengan mengurung anaknya Farid di dalam bilik agar tidak bercampur dengan orang lain. Tindakan itu telah membuatkan Farid menjadi seorang yang sangat pemalu dan takut untuk bergaul dengan masyarakat.

programme.title: Marah-Marah Sayang
programme.desc: Tiga jejaka yang cintakan muzik terpaksa dilepaskan dari kerja masing-masing kerana asyik leka dibuai irama ketika sedang bekerja yang menyebabkan ketidakselesaan orang lain. Rostam, Roslan dan Rosdin mula jatuh cinta terhadap tiga anak dara yang cantik namun Salina, Sarina dan Satina menolak cinta mereka. Pelbagai usaha telah dilakukan oleh mereka dan akhirnya mereka berjaya mengahwini gadis-gadis pilihan mereka itu. Syarat-syarat telah diberi jika ingin berkahwin namun telah dilanggar, ini telah mengakibatkan perkahwinan mereka menjadi kucar-kacir.

programme.title: Awang Spanar
programme.desc: Awang Spanar, gelaran yang diberi kerana kemahirannya yang pandai membaiki bot melalui pelbagai liku kehidupan bersama rakannya, Salleh. Percutian mereka di Kuala Lumpur bertukar menjadi sebuah pengembaraan apabila terlibat sebagai saksi kes penculikan. Sekumpulan mafia menculik anak hartawan bernama Rahim. Menjadi buruan mafia, mereka meminta bantuan seorang detektif, Lydia.

programme.title: Suara Kekasih
programme.desc: Percintaan yang ditentang keluarga kerana perbezaan darjat membuatkan Ayu dan Taufiq terpaksa membawa haluan berbeza. Ayu, penyanyi di kelab malam jatuh cinta dengan Taufiq, pengurus syarikat insuran yang berasal dari keluarga kaya. Ditentang oleh ibu Taufiq, mereka merasakan restu keluarga amat penting dan terpaksa membuat keputusan penting untuk masa depan mereka.

programme.title: Hero
programme.desc: Seorang pemuda bernama Os bekerja sebagai budak pejabat di sebuah syarikat insurans di ibu kota. Pada suatu hari berlaku satu kehilangan berlian di sebuah acara pameran. Os cuba menyelesaikan kes kehilangan berlian itu dengan bantuan seekor monyet yang menjadi sahabatnya.

programme.title: Dendang Remaja
programme.desc: Di sebuah akademi seni, terdapat dua kumpulan pelajar yang berseteru. Mereka tidak serius ketika belajar dan lebih menggemari muzik dari barat. Oleh kerana tidak mendapat bimbingan yang sewajarnya, para pelajar ini menjadi semakin liar sehingga menganggu ketenteraman.

programme.title: Tujuh Biang Keladi
programme.desc: Mona datang ke Kuala Lumpur untuk mencari pekerjaan setelah lari daripada rumah. Di Kuala Lumpur, dia tinggal serumah dengan enam orang gadis bujang dan mendapat kerja sebagai kerani. Oleh kerana memiliki raut wajah yang cantik, Mona mendapat ramai kenalan daripada orang berada yang sanggup membuat apa sahaja untuk dirinya. Pada masa yang sama, seorang murid bapa Mona yang bernama Mail telah datang mencarinya di Kuala Lumpur untuk membawanya pulang.

Syarat-syarat telah diberi jika ingin berkahwin namun telah dilanggar, ini telah mengakibatkan perkahwinan mereka menjadi kucar-kacir.

programme.title: Anaknya Sazali
programme.desc: Sazali tidak mahu anaknya mengamalkan pergaulan bebas sebagaimana yang pernah dilaluinya dahulu. Dia bertindak dengan mengurung anaknya Farid di dalam bilik agar tidak bercampur dengan orang lain. Tindakan itu telah membuatkan Farid menjadi seorang yang sangat pemalu dan takut untuk bergaul dengan masyarakat.

programme.title: Suara Kekasih
programme.desc: Percintaan yang ditentang keluarga kerana perbezaan darjat membuatkan Ayu dan Taufiq terpaksa membawa haluan berbeza. Ayu, penyanyi di kelab malam jatuh cinta dengan Taufiq, pengurus syarikat insuran yang berasal dari keluarga kaya. Ditentang oleh ibu Taufiq, mereka merasakan restu keluarga amat penting dan terpaksa membuat keputusan penting untuk masa depan mereka.

programme.title: Dendang Remaja
programme.desc: Di sebuah akademi seni, terdapat dua kumpulan pelajar yang berseteru. Mereka tidak serius ketika belajar dan lebih menggemari muzik dari barat. Oleh kerana tidak mendapat bimbingan yang sewajarnya, para pelajar ini menjadi semakin liar sehingga menganggu ketenteraman.

programme.title: Hero
programme.desc: Seorang pemuda bernama Os bekerja sebagai budak pejabat di sebuah syarikat insurans di ibu kota. Pada suatu hari berlaku satu kehilangan berlian di sebuah acara pameran. Os cuba menyelesaikan kes kehilangan berlian itu dengan bantuan seekor monyet yang menjadi sahabatnya.

programme.title: Tujuh Biang Keladi
programme.desc: Mona datang ke Kuala Lumpur untuk mencari pekerjaan setelah lari daripada rumah. Di Kuala Lumpur, dia tinggal serumah dengan enam orang gadis bujang dan mendapat kerja sebagai kerani. Oleh kerana memiliki raut wajah yang cantik, Mona mendapat ramai kenalan daripada orang berada yang sanggup membuat apa sahaja untuk dirinya. Pada masa yang sama, seorang murid bapa Mona yang bernama Mail telah datang mencarinya di Kuala Lumpur untuk membawanya pulang.

programme.title: Pening-Pening Lalat
programme.desc: Dino berjaya melarikan diri dari sebuah penjara dan sedang berada dalam buruan polis. Berita tentangnya mendapat liputan besar dan ditawarkan wang sebanyak RM10,000 kepada sesiapa yang menangkapnya. Mengetahui tentang itu, Dino mula menyembunyikan diri. Memutuskan untuk bersembunyi di hutan, Dino bertemu Zakaria dan Aliza.

programme.title: Dead Talents Society
programme.desc: Newbie ghost Rookie must fight to prove herself in the afterlife, where spirits are required to deliver spectacular scares to earn their place. Facing the threat of vanishing if she fails to secure a haunting license, she teams up with a washed-up ghost diva and her spectral agent, who train her to become the next star and stage the world's greatest fright.

programme.title: Chasing the Dragon
programme.desc: Infamous real-life drug kingpin Crippled Ho came to Hong Kong as an illegal immigrant in 1963 and ruthlessly built an empire from the chaotic underworld of drug dealers and corrupt police who ruled the city under notorious detective Lee Rock.

programme.title: iGirl
programme.desc: Evan, Johnny, and Irwin are best friends. All three of them get dumped by their girlfriends one day and decide to find three robotic substitutes, the iGirls, as their new girlfriends. However, as time goes by, Evan finds himself falling in love with his iGirl

programme.title: Fist of Legend
programme.desc: When Chen Zhen studies in Japan, he finds several Chinese students missing and accidentally uncovers the Black Dragon Society's conspiracy. A new drug is invented to boost bodies of the Japanese troops in war and the Chinese students are used in their experiments. Chen Zhen vows to take down the evil society and destroy their secret laboratory.

programme.title: Once in a Blue Moon
programme.desc: Mei Zhen's family appears to get along but harbours deep secrets. Mei Zhen is trapped in a dead-end job with a toxic boss, her brother hides his separation and their mother grapples with lingering guilt over her husband's departure years ago. As Mid-Autumn Festival approaches, can the family heal their wounds and find a way back to each other?

programme.title: The Monkey King 3
programme.desc: Monkey King, Pigsy and Sandy escort Monk Tang to retrieve the scriptures and accidentally head into the mysterious Female Kingdom. The Queen falls in love with Monk Tang at first sight, but her advisor orders Monk Tang and his disciples to be executed. As the four attract the appearance of River Spirit, the Female Kingdom is plunged into crisis!

programme.title: Love is Blind, Hate Too
programme.desc: Bo lost her eye sight in a serious car accident a year ago. One day, she is left alone at home when her husband is away on a work trip. An intruder enters Bo's house and takes her hostage. As Bo tries to survive his mental and psychological torture, she discovers her husband's secret which is related to the accident leading to her blindness

programme.title: The Last Tycoon
programme.desc: Gangster Chen Da Qi rises to the upper echelons of power, but finds himself torn between the love of two women, the murderous plots of the secret service, and the looming threat of war.

programme.title: Fight Back to School
programme.desc: The number one killer in SDU, Chow Sing Sing(Stephen Chow), is sent to a school to find a lost gun. His partner Tat(Ng Man Tat) pretends to be a school worker in assisting him. They recognize that some students are being closed with Fei, the head of triad society, and Fei traffics munitions. Sing steals and ignites Fei's munitions, Fei pledges to kill Sing...

programme.title: Sex and the Beauties
programme.desc: It is said that Hong Kong is a sexy and sexual city where life is breathtakingly fast but glamorous. Fear of marriage, single & successful psychiatrist, Selina and other beauties seek for love and happy endings.

programme.title: Acting Out of Love
programme.desc: Wei Hung Jen is a struggling actor who gets fired but finds a job behind the scene. Hui Hsin, the associate producer, must write a script for a love story so as to get a reference letter to study scriptwriting overseas. As Jen falls for Hui, he invites her out on a date as a research for her script and they start acting out of love.

programme.title: The Grey Men 2
programme.desc: Triad boss Song seeks to whitewash his image and seize Laika's mayoral seat amid a regime change. He faces a funding shortfall despite colluding with officials, and gets his right-hand man and enforcer to commit crimes to boost his funds and power. Just as Song believes success is imminent, the dynamics between the three take an unexpected turn

programme.title: Ah Boys to Men
programme.desc: Ken is a rich and spoiled young man reluctant to be enlisted into National Service but must do so by law. He has to endure harsh training but it is made more bearable when he befriends three other recruits. When his girlfriend breaks up with him, Ken tries all ways to escape from camp so as to chase her back, but this leads to dire consequences

programme.title: High Forces
programme.desc: On its maiden flight, an A380 airliner is hijacked by armed gunmen. Among the passengers is international security expert Gao Hao Jun, whose daughter has been taken hostage, putting her life in grave danger. Determined to save her, Gao confronts the hijackers head-on. Can he rescue all the passengers and thwart the crisis?

programme.title: Rob N Roll
programme.desc: A ruthless bandit, Tian, has plotted an intense and quick armed robbery. When he encounters Hui and Shui who also plan for a robbery, they decide to team up for the heist. However, their ad-hoc and dramatic robbery has started a war with the police hot on pursuit, putting their lives on the line!

programme.title: Initial D
programme.desc: The movie is adapted from a famous Japanese manga. 18-year-old Takumi delivers tofu in his father's near-obsolete car every day and becomes a good racer with perfect drifting skill. Encouraged by his father, he joins a mountain race and unexpectedly wins it, making him famous overnight and leading him from one exciting race to another.

programme.title: Lucky Star 2015
programme.desc: When a talent manager meets a guy whose voice resembles the famous comedian Stephen Chow, things starts to stir up in the show biz. "Lucky Star 2015" is a hilarious comedy starring actors from both Hong Kong and Taiwan, including Eric Tsang, Dada Chan and Wong Cho Lam.

programme.title: Cyber Heist
programme.desc: Hackers have caused a large-scale cyber attack, but luckily cyber security engineer Chun, manages to fend it off with his protective firewall system. To Chun's surprise, his boss is the mastermind of the attack, and when Chun gets trapped in a money laundering operation, he must fight against his boss in the cyber world to prove his innocence.

programme.title: I Love Hong Kong
programme.desc: Ng Shun and his family return to the public housing estate where he grew up, not to visit his aging father, but to seek refuge after his business has failed. When his family of five squeeze into the small estate unit, Ng Shun is forced to face his long-neglected family problems...

programme.title: Echoes Of The Thunder
programme.desc: Two half-brothers, Nam and Fire, are top racing drivers. In a racing challenge with Japanese driver Kenji, Nam causes a young racing driver to be seriously injured and is depressed. Fire stands up for Nam and decides to compete with Kenji in an illegal street car race. Who will win the race? Can Nam finally bounce back?

programme.title: MuMu
programme.desc: Mumu, a cheerful seven-year-old girl, lives with her deaf father in a deaf community and connects him to the outside world. However, their peaceful life is disrupted when her estranged mother reappears, pushing Mumu into the hearing world. Meanwhile, her father becomes ensnared by a gang that exploits the deaf to commit crimes.

programme.title: The Moon Thieves
programme.desc: A crooked watch dealer assembles a daring crew - a thief, an explosive expert, a lock breaker and a watch connoisseur - to steal three luxury watches in Tokyo. Their mission takes an unexpected turn when they discover the legendary 'Moonwatch.' Pursued by the yakuza, the team must unite to navigate the chaos and pull off their high-stakes heist.

programme.title: From Vegas To Macau II
programme.desc: Mark, the chief accountant of a money-laundering syndicate, has stolen US$15 billion from the fund and absconded to Thailand with his daughter. Interpol agent Lok seeks help from Ken, the God of Gamblers, to capture the syndicate's mastermind. As they search for Mark to testify in the case, Ken reunites with the love of his life

programme.title: God Of Gamblers 2
programme.desc: A new chapter of the highly successful "God of Gamblers". The legend's disciple Andy Lau is now rising in the gambling world as the "Knight of Gamblers", clashing with another gambling icon, the wild psychic Stephen Chow (aka "Saint of Gamblers") who wants to follow the God. They mix like oil and water in a series of tricks and mishaps, but are forced to join hands against their master's nemesis on the gambling table.

programme.title: All U Need Is Love
programme.desc: Ten major film companies join forces on a comedy-drama film to raise funds and create jobs for industry workers during the COVID-19 pandemic. This film features an all-star ensemble cast starring for free, with the story revolving around a group of hotel guests placed under quarantine in Hong Kong.

programme.title: Mission Milano
programme.desc: A wealthy entrepreneur goes undercover with an Interpol agent to protect a new invention, the Seed of God, from falling into an international crime conglomerate.

programme.title: Mama's Affair
programme.desc: Former talent manager Mei Fung stays home to take care of her husband and son after retirement. She decides to re-enter the entertainment business to find her value in life, and successfully transforms a local restaurant delivery boy, Fong Ching, into a young pop idol. This makes her teenage son, Jonathan, intensely jealous of Fong Ching.

programme.title: Quan Dao: The Journey of a Boxer
programme.desc: Ah Niu learns boxing from Uncle Xing, the boss of a boxing studio, since young and uses his skills to help the weak fight villains. When Xing's son attempts drug trafficking to save his father's studio but fails and is brutally beaten up, Ah Niu accepts a death combat challenge so as to help him take revenge.

programme.title: Far Far Away
programme.desc: A 28-year-old IT geek has only been in love once. Surprisingly, he ends up getting romantically involved with five different women this year and the one thing they have in common is that they all live in far flung areas of Hong Kong. After taking five intensive relationship courses within these 365 days, will he find the-one?

programme.title: Vanguard
programme.desc: A businessman Qin Guo Li is being kidnapped in London and his daughter is also in danger. The international security team, Vanguard, is hired to rescue them. Tang Huan Ting, the founder, gathers an elite team to track them down across countries, from London to Africa and Dubai. In the process, they also discover another dangerous conspiracy.

programme.title: Lonely Eighteen
programme.desc: Set in the 1980s Hong Kong, Elaine and her best friend Ying enter the entertainment industry hoping to change their fates from poverty. Ying soon becomes a popular porn star but Elaine is lost between being her true self and an actress. When show business declines after a decade, their choices lead them to two different paths in life.

programme.title: The Wandering Earth II
programme.desc: In this prequel, humans build enormous engines on the Earth's surface to find a new home when the sun is burning out. In the dangerous universe, a group of young people has to step forward once again to fight in the critical battle to save the Earth.

programme.title: The Brave Archer 3
programme.desc: Guo Jing and Huang Rong go to Iron Palm Peak to search for the Book of Wumu. The chief of Iron Palm discovers their visit, and seriously injures Huang. It seems only the Southern Emperor Duan can heal her, but will Huang be healed in time?

programme.title: Madam White Snake
programme.desc: Linda Lin Dai is perfect as Pak Su-cheng, the stunning snake goddess who assumes a womanly form so that she can taste the pleasures of a human life! Pak seduces young scholar, Hsu Hsien when she recognises him as her saviour in another life 1,000 years ago. But when Buddhist monk Fa Hai finds out about the union, the pair is forced to split...

programme.title: The Blood Brothers
programme.desc: The friendship of three sworn brothers, Zhang, Huang and Ma ends when Ma gives in to corruption and falls for Huang's wife, eventually leading to a bloody ending.

programme.title: The Empress Dowager
programme.desc: Award-winning drama featuring a passionate performance by Lisa Lu, enhanced by sumptuous costumes and sets, produces a powerful, fascinating story. In five thousand years of Chinese history, there was never a more fascinating woman than the dragon lady of the Ching Dynasty, also the Empress Dowager, who was the power behind the throne for the last half of the 19th century. The vast tapestry of palace intrigues is vividly brought to the screen.

programme.title: The Killer
programme.desc: Hsieh Choun, the Black Dragon, is in trouble with the police since Wang Sien Tien's gang is helping them, he is no longer free to conduct his drugs shipments out of the port freely as he used to. He buys more thugs and killers to dispose of the young upstart, and soon Wang is in dire straits, in the port of Hong Kong.

programme.title: The Mirror and the Lichee
programme.desc: The curious title in this Huangmei Opera romance refers to the two props that signal a happy beginning between a scholar and a local beauty. The scholar polishes mirrors so as to be closer to his love, who signals her approval by tossing him some lichees. From that point on the course of their love becomes rocky, complete with murder and suicide.

programme.title: Flying Guillotine 2
programme.desc: In a time of anti-Manchu sentiment, Emperor Yong Zheng employs his ruthless Blood Hound Corps to silence any dissenters. Only one man and his signature weapon, The Flying Guillotine, stand in their way.

programme.title: Les Belles
programme.desc: Acknowledged as one of the greatest Hong Kong musicals, this lavish movie starring Linda Lin, who won Best Actress for her performance, infuses its wispy plot with style and wit, and the results are pure pleasure.

programme.title: The Long Chase
programme.desc: Governor Yan is killed and his guard Fan identifies Kou as the assassin by his signature weapon, a dart. Kou is listed as a wanted man when he enters the city, but managed to escape arrest with the help of the innkeeper's daughter. At the same time, Fan is attacked by a bandit who pretends to be Kou. What are the secret plots behind these attacks?

programme.title: Rose, Be My Love
programme.desc: Not a love triangle but a love 'rectangle', Rose, Be My Love is a romantic drama set on the eve of World War II that represents the high standards achieved by Shaw Brothers in both aspects of star power and technical polish.

programme.title: Return of Reincarnated Swordsman
programme.desc: A band of ninjas slaughters the entire Wu Dang Clan and frames Du Gu Wu Di, chief of the Invincible Clan, for the deed. Yun masters the silkworm martial arts style and decides to take revenge for the Clan by challenging Wu Di, but is defeated and seriously hurt. Luckily, Master Li saves and treats him, allowing Yun to avoid the ninjas' pursuit.

programme.title: Crazy Shaolin Disciples
programme.desc: The story revolves around three lay disciples of the Shaolin Temple: Fang Shi Yu, Hong Xi Guan, and Hu Hui Qian. Monk Jie instructs them in martial arts, but their frequent competitions with fellow disciple Wu Qing spark rivalries. The once serene Shaolin Temple is plunged into chaos, yet even the abbot cannot help but be amused by their antics.

programme.title: To Kill a Jaguar
programme.desc: Set in 1920s Shanghai, a village girl journeys to the big city in search of her father and meets her childhood friend Jaguar, who works for the mob boss Kam. In a world controlled by the mobs, it is a test of survival for all as Jaguar allies himself with ace gunman Ko Tang, to take over Kam's empire.

programme.title: The Snake Prince
programme.desc: The Snake Prince lives on the Snake Mountain of Kwangsi with other snakes and they have lived peacefully with humans for a thousand years. All things change however, when the Snake Prince falls in love with one of the three beauties performing a sensual rain dance in the nearby village one day, and decides to marry her at all costs...

programme.title: The Enchantress
programme.desc: Shot on the Shaws' lot in the final years of Hong Kong's greatest studio, The Enchantress tells the story of martial artists who disappear in the night! Intrigued, wanna-be detective/swordsman Feng Chi-wu (Mok Siu-chung) is determined to find out what is happening. But when Feng finds out that an evil vampire spirit (Wei Chiu-hua) is killing swordsmen, he's in for more than he bargains for... It's an outlandish fairy-tale and martial arts fantasy, where your fists and sword aren't nearly enough!

programme.title: The Last Tempest
programme.desc: This sequel to The Empress Dowager continues the tale of Emperor Guangxu and Empress Dowager Cixi. Despite Guangxu's enthronement, his ability to rule effectively is overshadowed by the ever-present power of Cixi. When his attempts to reform the Imperial system are thwarted by the Empress Dowager, Guangxu attempts to curb her power.

programme.title: The Chinese Boxer
programme.desc: A Japanese karate master and Diao Er, who has been expelled from his martial arts school, return to the school to kill the school master and his disciples. After the massacre, disciple Lei Ming embarks on a vigorous training regime and vows to avenge their deaths. A fatal battle is about to begin

programme.title: Young Lovers
programme.desc: Guitar-playing rich kid, Yang Fan, heads to Japan to join a rock 'n' roll band where he soon finds himself competing for the affections of two beautiful girls.

programme.title: The Mighty One
programme.desc: Lung seeks five volumes of a renowned Kung Fu manual to gain invincibility. When he believes a martial arts school master possesses the volumes, he kills him and his daughter but leaves behind a young brother and sister. Years later, Lung loses two volumes and starts another bloody hunt but each attempt is interrupted by two mysterious warriors...

programme.title: The Shepherd Girl
programme.desc: In this musical drama, Hsiu Hsiu, a beautiful shepherd girl, falls in love with a handsome boatman Ta Lung. However, she cannot afford to marry him because of her father's towering debt from gambling. To complicate the matter, a rival suitor promises to pay off all her father's debts on one condition: that Hsiu Hsiu marries him...

programme.title: Heaven Sword and Dragon Sabre 2
programme.desc: Only by bringing together the powerful Heaven Sword and the mighty Dragon Sabre can six martial arts sects struggling for supremacy be saved in this thrilling sequel to Chu Yuan's original hit.

programme.title: The Younger Generation
programme.desc: A tragic tale about a young girl who gets married and has five kids. When she and her husband die, leaving all five kids behind to fend for themselves, the eldest child is forced to be sold into prostitution to feed the other four.

programme.title: That Fiery Girl
programme.desc: The bandits of Hulu Valley slay the chief of the Mei Clan while searching for a treasure map. In retaliation, Chun from the Mei Clan infiltrates the bandit's fortress to map a way in for the authorities, but ends up falling in love with the bandit leader's daughter, Pearl. While Chun's plot is uncovered, he receives unexpected help from Pearl.

programme.title: Diau Charn
programme.desc: In the Han Dynasty, the tyrannical Prime Minister Dong Zuo takes control of the country, so Minister Wang plots to take him down using Diau Charn's beauty. Wang arranges for her to be Dong's concubine as he knows Dong's adopted son Lu Bu is in love with her, turning them against each other. Lu Bu ends up killing Dong Zuo to be with Diau Charn.

programme.title: Facets Of Love
programme.desc: Set in the Ming Dynasty, the story revolves around a brothel and the girls who work there. The film begins by following the life of a girl from a poor family, who is sold by her mother to the brothel. While she is the most beautiful of the girls and attracts many clients, the girl hopes to escape this sad way of life one day.

programme.title: The Land of Many Perfumes
programme.desc: Monk Tang San Zang, Monkey, Pigsy and Sha Wu Jing find themselves in Womanland, where women only give birth to baby girls and do so by drinking the magical spring water.

programme.title: The Lark
programme.desc: Sixties pop star Carrie Ku plays the "Little Lark" in this romantic-drama of mistaken identity that is a treasure trove of some of the most popular Mandarin songs of all time.

programme.title: Heroes Two
programme.desc: Shaolin disciple Hong escapes from the burning temple after it is attacked by the Qing army and is badly wounded. He is handed over to the Qing soldiers by Fang as he mistakes Hong for a bandit. When Fang realizes his mistakes, he tries all ways to help Hong escape so that they can team up to fight the Qing army together.

programme.title: Forever And Ever
programme.desc: Ivy Ling Po plays a young scholar who is manipulated into marrying a nobleman's reluctant daughter. After marrying, he soon discovers the reason for her hesitation. She is stricken with a contagious disease. But, with the power of true love, their romance prevails.

programme.title: The Spiritual Boxer
programme.desc: One of the first kung fu comedies, this is a story about a con artist who uses kung fu to swindle villagers for money by pretending to be possessed by spirits. When they are threatened by bandits, he must use the same skills for good.

programme.title: The Pearl Phoenix
programme.desc: In Huangmei Opera tradition, this movie tells the love story of Wen, who sells himself as a slave to a rich family, and Huo, the family's young daughter. The lovers are kept apart by Huo's stepmother and Huo escapes by dressing up as a man. Wen is framed and put into jail so Huo has to go back and rescue her lover!

programme.title: The Lizard
programme.desc: A seasoned burglar 'The Lizard' sets himself up against a corrupt police chief and announced that he will steal a diamond from a rich man's party. His real identity, which is discovered by the corrupt police chief's granddaughter, is actually a young policeman who is doing it all for justice.

programme.title: Gossip Street
programme.desc: All neighbours gather to gossip in flat number 8 on the second floor of the Gossip Street apartment building! Most of the residents are common people from all walks of life and there is never a lack of laughter or sarcasm in the neighbourhood. However, when a local mobster wants to change the place into a gambling den, things get serious...

programme.title: The New One-Armed Swordsman
programme.desc: David Chiang plays the all-new one-armed hero - a swordsman who chops off his right arm rather than live with dishonour. When the love of his life is kidnapped and his best friend is murdered by the evil gang, it is time to battle.

programme.title: The Big Sting
programme.desc: Three buddies find a rare artifact known as the Double-Faced God but are poisoned by Lady Wu who steals the treasure from them. Before they die, they get their wives to promise to train their children to take back what is rightfully theirs. These kids grow up to exact a vengeance that turns out to be more hilarious than horrific in this comedy.
